Facebook to Get Privacy Audits for 20 Years Under Settlement With U.S. FTC

-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 
2011-11-29T17:42:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-29/facebook-to-get-privacy-audits-for-20-years-under-settlement-with-u-s-ftc.html
Facebook agreed to get periodic
assessments of its privacy practices by independent auditors for
the next 20 years as part of a settlement of Federal Trade
Commission claims that the company deceived consumers about
sharing of information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  